A lush tropical botanical garden scene in Studio Ghibli style, featuring an intimate corner where exotic orchids with impossibly vivid fuchsia and gold petals spiral around ancient moss-covered stones. Dappled sunlight filters through towering palm fronds and giant fern leaves, creating pools of warm golden light on a winding path. A curious small bird with iridescent feathers perches on a twisted vine, while delicate butterflies drift lazily through humid air thick with visible moisture droplets. The composition suggests hidden discoveries around every corner, with mysterious shadowy pathways leading deeper into verdant green depths. Soft, dreamy color palette with rich emeralds, deep teals, and warm amber highlights characteristic of animated fantasy forests.
